General.Name: RVRC Holding AB
General.Description: RVRC Holding AB (publ) provides active lifestyle clothing in Sweden. It offers pants, jackets, tops, mid layers, and base layers apparels; and bags and backpacks, as well as accessories, such as underwear, socks, shoes, hats, beanies, belts, gloves, collars, neck warmers, miscellaneous outdoor and hiking products, and other accessories through online stores. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Borås, Sweden.
